Finally, we can raid properly.
<p>
One final thing, before ending this update.&nbsp; Many are
familiar I'm sure with the Clockwork Talisman quest (summarized <a
href="http://pub146.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showMessage?topicID=6034.topic"><font
